OpenCLI Scraper — OpenComputer Plugin
======================================

This plugin wraps OpenCLI, which is licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0.

OpenCLI
  Copyright 2025 jackwener
  https://github.com/jackwener/opencli
  License: Apache-2.0

This plugin does not modify OpenCLI source code. It invokes the OpenCLI
binary as a subprocess and adds rate limiting, robots.txt enforcement,
and per-adapter field whitelisting on top.

